					.featured-box-col2.fadeInRight.delay
						h3 Event Photographs
						p Capture your events whether professional or casual.
				.featured-box
					.featured-box-col1.fadeInRight.delay
						i class="fa-group"
					.featured-box-col2.fadeInRight.delay
						h3 Boudoir
						p Give a special gift to your special someone
				a class="Learn-More" href="#" Learn More

section class="main-section team" id="about"
	.ui.container
		h2 I'm Nick
		<h6>A bit about who I am and why I love photography.
		.team-leader-block clearfix"
			.team-leader-box"
				.wow fadeInDown delay"
					= image_tag("nick.jpg")
				h3 class="wow fadeInDown delay" Nick Coffey
				span class="wow fadeInDown delay" Lead Photographer, Owner
				p class="wow fadeInDown delay" 
					| I'm pretty good at photos.  They are fun to take and I will take them of you if you want.
			.team-leader-box
				p class="wow fadeInDown delay"
					| As a native, I have spent plenty of time experiencing the many sights and sounds that Colorado has to offer. I enjoy getting up to the high country, be it for skiing, snowboarding, or just to enjoy all the great landscapes. I'm a big fan of backyard barbecues, relaxing at a park, or checking out one of the many breweries Denver has to offer. Whatever it may be, I enjoy taking it all in, and am always toting my camera around to capture it.
			.team-leader-box
				p class="wow fadeInDown delay"
					| I'm always excited to sit down and work with new clients.  I love all types of projects and enjoy a new challenge everyday. Maybe it's capturing those little smirks a bride shares when she sees her husband for the first time on their wedding day. It's about making something as memorable as possible, or portraying a certain message through a photograph.  I'm always ready for an adventure or to seek out that perfect spot for a shoot. It's always a journey, and I would absolutely love the opportunity to capture your day.

